{"tid":1652273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(apm勇士) 各位手足做咩大茶飯都好 做好以下幾點保平安 唔想大家畀狗咬","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:23:30.000Z","uid":4322,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f6dcaef29ea7f61ff8f27baf4724549e446fc944","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"希望各位想效法apm勇士既手足<br />\n做咩大茶飯都要做以下幾點<br />\n勇士勇氣可嘉 但手法未夠完美 要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係我觀查所得要注意事項<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n1）包好全身連鞋 不解釋*<br />\n2）揀岩落手位置及時機 落單狗/夜晚/一唔為意先落手/最好休班狗（老豆搵仔）<br />\n3）事前行熟撤退路線 防止慌不擇路 <br />\n4）同朋友練熟落手時既動作 遇到反擊要點做 務求一擊即中要害 <br />\n5）最好book埋機票即晚就走 避風頭<br />\n6）戴假髮 紋身貼紙 混淆視聽 配合第一點自己執生<br />\n7）搵信得過朋友帶衫畀你換/接放學<br />\n8）混入人堆盡快撤退</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e5d0e0ab53cc63bab8c73489fced326ecb136d6d","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"ab6ea0c1ba06c602a32a4b16aed33c5ecbf8fbd1","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"790b96fa4d749dd4f49a7fded055c2ce3120024b","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"6ab9a2b57ac92e475a4356d3c4f963c8e5585dce","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"fa79cab5fd9ea01602d76347d143eeda578b62a8","tid":1652273,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"4a837f3ac19c5ed7741ff04f21dcab547ff5fd4a","tid":1652273,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2470